	bug filed as radar #10302855 from __gnat_error_handler to...
	(__gnat_adjust_context_for_raise) [Darwin]: ...here.  New function.
	(HAVE_GNAT_ADJUST_CONTEXT_FOR_RAISE) [Darwin]: Define.

