	possibility of this flag being set for formals in Ada 2012 mode.
	* par-ch6.adb (P_Formal_Part): Handle aliased for parameters for Ada
	2012.
	* sem_ch6.adb (Process_Formals): Handle aliased parameters in Ada 2012
	mode.
