	processing of TSS routine Finalize_Address when compiling in
	CodePeer_Mode.

2011-08-29  Thomas Quinot  <quinot@adacore.com>

	* a-strunb.ads, einfo.ads, g-comlin.ads, sem_ch6.adb,
	sem_warn.adb: Minor reformatting.

