	* gcc-interface/Makefile.in (raise-gcc.o): Fix previous change.

	* gcc-interface/gigi.h (enumerate_modes): Fix formatting.

	* gcc-interface/trans.c (Subprogram_Body_to_gnu): Revert latest change.

