2011-08-02  Geert Bosch  <bosch@adacore.com>

	* opt.ads
	(Preprocessing_Symbol_Defs): Move from Prepcomp.Symbol_Definitions.
	(Preprocessing_Symbol_Last): Move from Prepcomp.Last_Definition.
